data.description: Solid Traditional 4-sided Brick - with extra square footage everywhere - including the Level Lot of 1.23 acres.  This Home, minutes from Conyers shopping, is complemented with a very large Screened-In Porch and Deck for year around outside enjoyment.  A partially wooded yard offers summer shade to minimize the Summer Heat.  The Interior starts with a Foyer , Formal Living and Dining Rooms which wrap into a long country Kitchen with white cabinets and a comfortable Breakfast Area for extra space at meal times.  Extending on is an Oversized Family Room featuring a Brick Fireplace and Wet Bar for evening relaxing and entertaining.  Tucked in the middle of the Main Floor is a large Bedroom and a Full Bath.  The Upper Level has a Full Bath and two huge Bedrooms with oversized closets.  Additionally, the En Suite has most of the Upper Level with a Sitting Area, 8 x 8 Walk In Closet, Separate Tub and Shower Bathroom and enough room left over for a Kingsized Bed and oversized Furniture.  The side entry 2 Car Garage has a Finished Bonus Room above with a separate Inside entrance.
